<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports creating a customized ToolTip on a chart</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>


<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Legend ToolTip"</Bold> enables or disables the ToolTip of a chart legend. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Chart ToolTip"</Bold> enables or disables the ToolTip of a chart. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Chart Area ToolTip"</Bold> enables or disables the ToolTip of a chart area. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Chart Series ToolTip"</Bold> enables or disables the chart series ToolTip. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Radio button <Bold>"Default Content"</Bold> includes the default content to the ToolTip </Paragraph>
</ListItem>


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Radio button <Bold>"Customized Content"</Bold> includes the customized content to the ToolTip </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>

</FlowDocument>